cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Deployer AI Risk Register (DARR)"
message: "If you use this register, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
abstract: >-
  An open, citable AI risk register for organizations that deploy AI systems:
  82 canonical risks and 61 MITRE ATLAS-anchored sub-risks across seven families,
  consolidated from the MIT AI Risk Repository and mapped to ISO/IEC 23894 and
  42001, MITRE ATLAS, and the EU AI Act, then cross-checked against IBM, Cisco,
  NIST, and OWASP. Published under CC BY 4.0.
authors:
  - name: "MindXO"
    website: "https://www.mind-xo.com"
version: "1.0"
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.21223593
date-released: "2026-07-03"
license: CC-BY-4.0
url: "https://www.airiskdeployer.org"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Myr-Aya/darr-deployer-ai-risk-register"
keywords:
  - AI risk
  - AI governance
  - AI safety
  - risk register
  - MITRE ATLAS
  - EU AI Act
  - ISO/IEC 42001
  - NIST AI RMF
  - responsible AI
  - LLM security
